## Exclude Flutter artifacts (Vercel deploys Next.js only)
flutter_app/.dart_tool
flutter_app/build
flutter_app/.flutter-plugins
flutter_app/.flutter-plugins-dependencies

## Android/iOS build artifacts inside flutter_app
flutter_app/android/.gradle
flutter_app/android/**/build
flutter_app/ios/Pods
flutter_app/ios/.symlinks
flutter_app/ios/Flutter/Flutter.framework
flutter_app/ios/Flutter/Flutter.podspec

## Next build outputs (generated on Vercel)
.next
out

## Local storage + misc
/storage/
.vercel

## Local secrets
*.pem
*service-account*.json
*firebase-adminsdk*.json
firebase-admin.json
